      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AMREN (1) quickly into stride and found the front, leading until late when third (19.90) at this track in a Free For All over 352m. Goes well out of this box with a win and five minor placings. Leading chance again. MILO DAVIS (8) shapes well for this on his slick win a few runs back, getting around Q Straight over 300m in 16.56 then hitting the frame in both runs since. Has the ability and can find winning form again. GRANDIOSE GIRL (2) is better than last start when fifth (20.01) in a Free For All at this track over 352m. Form here at the trip sound including eight wins. One of the main contenders. EXPELLED (7) has won at this course and distance so worth including.",
